text:
Central Park West, 102nd Street, to lost Street, (Before Reconstruction).

March 22, 1920.
title: Manhattan: Central Park West - 101st Street

text:
Central Park: The Pool, on the west side, near 101st Street, showing seven wild geese in the water. This pool empties into the Loch, which in turn drains into Harlem Mere.

1923.

P. L. Sperr.
title: Manhattan: Central Park - The Pond.
